      <bioghist id="aspace_fc711f358f24d5102a93e3f3e0ba68c5">
         <head>Robin McDouall (b. 1908)</head>
         <p>Robin McDouall, British author of books on cooking and dining.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_b035ba8e38d7fc0dc245c8a7b7e62169">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of letters received by McDouall from his friends Harold Acton, Patrick Leigh Fermor, Evie Hone, John Sparrow, Cecil Woodham Smith, and others. They are personal in nature and include many invitations and thank-you notes. Also present is one photograph of two unidentified men.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
